{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/divide-the-grid-into-an-area-template","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"css-grid","demoType":null,"title":"Gawanya gridi kuwa eneo la template","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Možete spojiti ćelije svoje mreže zajedno u <dfn>oblast </dfn> i dati toj oblasti jedinstveno ime. To učinite korišćenjem <code>grid-template-areas</code> na kontejneru, kao što sledi:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">grid-template-areas:\r\n  'header header header'\r\n  'advert content content'\r\n  'advert footer footer';\n</code></pre>\n<p>Gornji kod povezuje ćelije mreže u četiri područja: <code>header</code>, <code>advert</code>, <code>content</code>, na <code>footer</code>. Svaka reč predstavlja jednu ćeliju, a svaki par navodnika predstavlja jedan red.</p>\n</section>","id":"5a94fe0569fb03452672e45c","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Promenite šablon tako da oblast <code>footer</code> pokrije ceo donji red. Napomena: Ove oblasti trenutno ne mogu izazvati vidljiv efekat. Kasnije, koristićete funkciju kako biste videli kako funkcioniše korišćenjem te oblasti.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301130,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/divide-the-grid-into-an-area-template"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\r\n  .item1 {\r\n    background: LightSkyBlue;\r\n  }\r\n  .item2 {\r\n    background: LightSalmon;\r\n  }\r\n  .item3 {\r\n    background: PaleTurquoise;\r\n  }\r\n  .item4 {\r\n    background: LightPink;\r\n  }\r\n  .item5 {\r\n    background: PaleGreen;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .container {\r\n    font-size: 40px;\r\n    min-height: 300px;\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    background: LightGray;\r\n    display: grid;\r\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\r\n    grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\r\n    grid-gap: 10px;\r\n    grid-template-areas:\r\n    /* Only change code below this line */\r\n      'header header header'\r\n      'advert content content'\r\n      'advert footer footer';\r\n    /* Only change code above this line */\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n  <div class=\"item1\">1</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item2\">2</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item3\">3</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item4\">4</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item5\">5</div>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Klasa za <code>container</code> bi trebalo da ima svojstvo <code>grid-template-areas</code> kao primer, ali sa oblastima/regionom <code>footer</code> koji pokriva ceo donji red.</p>","testString":"assert.match(\r\n  __helpers.removeCssComments(code),\r\n  /.container\\s*?{[\\s\\S]*grid-template-areas\\s*?:\\s*?[\"|']\\s*?header\\s*?header\\s*?header\\s*?[\"|']\\s*?[\"|']\\s*?advert\\s*?content\\s*?content\\s*?[\"|']\\s*?[\"|']\\s*?footer\\s*?footer\\s*?footer\\s*?[\"|']\\s*?;[\\s\\S]*}/gi\r\n);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#css-grid","dashedName":"divide-the-grid-into-an-area-template","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"css-grid","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/place-items-in-grid-areas-using-the-grid-area-property","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/align-all-items-vertically-using-align-items","id":"5a94fe0569fb03452672e45c","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"cha